commit.title: [gramlib] Don't expose unsafe interfaces to clients
commit.message:
[gramlib] Don't expose unsafe interfaces to clients

I'd say this is more of a temporary measure than a long-term plan; IMO
we should make the interfaces safe so `Gramlib.Grammar` does provide
only one signature.
